Author: johnleema
Title: [ANN][ICO] ICONIC - An ICOs ecosystem built through Decentralized Assurance
Body: Iconic is an ecosystem for the financing and offering of businesses’ assets through blockchain technology. Using the potential of decentralized trust to drive by financing promising businesses, Iconic joins the market while its evolution and popularization occurs exponentially. To successfully enter such an effervescent and competitive market, Iconic's ecosystem is presented as the most complete so far, covering all possible phases of an ICO: the offering of tokens; the trading of successfully offered tokens; and the necessary instruments to guarantee the fulfilment of promises and obligations made in the offers. Through the three different parts of its ecosystem, Iconic presents a complete environment for investments in impacting businesses, with security related services and guarantees never seen before in the market. We then call the community through the "Let's move the chains" campaign, offering the Iconic ecosystem to, together, create an integrated, stable and secure path for technology to achieve its full potential.

Title: [ANN][ICO] ICONIC - An ICOs ecosystem built through Decentralized Assurance
Body: Iconic is developed to help the organisations for trading solutions by using block chain technology. This company established to guide and enhance the trading skills and help developing the new borns in investment market in the world of blockchain and other trusted market chain. Iconic has come up at its best with a splendid technology to address the investment market needs as there was no other leader has been classified to help developing in retail. Irrespective of how small or big the investment is, the private investment contracts demand for the conflicting cost with risk return offers in the traditional market.  Though they are acutely legislative they are also offering investors little liquidity which happens to drop down their rate of investment.  The block chain and distributed trust technologies brought a transformation in this investment world by employing the electronic assets honestly and has come forth over Initial Coin Offerings (ICO). More than 2 billion dollars were collected to fund the various ventures in exchange for all kind of tokens, for the time period of 2016-2017. Like never before this Crowd Investment in electronic assets contributed in enhancing in worlds dynamism, productivity, liquidity and translucence.

Link to previous work:  https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1O3CRCW2slhfWSHofFS0XEh8IeBUhuO1M  About Malay Language:  MALAY (Malaysian) language is widely used primarily in Malaysia, Singapore, Brunei, part of Indonesia & the Philippines), it is somewhat similar to, but distinctly different than the Indonesian language.  See excerpt from Wikipedia here -->     Malay (/məˈleɪ/; Malay: Bahasa Melayu بهاس ملايو) is a major language of the Austronesian family spoken in Malaysia, Singapore, Brunei, and Indonesia. It is spoken by 290 million people across the Strait of Malacca, including the coasts of the Malay Peninsula of Malaysia and the eastern coast of Sumatra in Indonesia, and has been established as a native language of part of western coastal Sarawak and West Kalimantan in Borneo. It is also used as a trading language in the southern Philippines, including the southern parts of the Zamboanga Peninsula, the Sulu Archipelago and the southern municipalities of Bataraza and Balabac in Palawan.

Author: joiniconic
Title: [ANN][ICO] ICONIC - An ICOs ecosystem built through Decentralized Assurance
Body: Hello, let's start with the first question:  1 Thinking of Iconic as a mere Ico-launch-environment is not a precise approach on how we built the entire project.  Iconic was thought to improve the entire ICO market as self-sufficient environment, meaning that it was built to provide not only the technical and business (including those provided by third parties, as environment managers) tools to launch ICOs, but also a place do have those bought tokens traded and specially instruments of assurance to the whole cycle of life of projects-businesses.  There is no way of having a safe and sound ICO environment without instruments for assurance, such as audits, escrowing and arbitrations.  And Iconic will provide them to the market, aiming to help it develop and achieve a new level.  2 Our token - NIC - has a very unique design.  It was built to have a lot of utilities within Iconic's evosystem, such as participating in exclusive ICOs or having a date reservation to participante in ICOs; buying some specific licenses Iconic will auction, etc.  But we think that our big differential is the DAO Fund to be built, planned to be NIC's ballast. The DAO fund will provide the finantial amount of support for the NIC so it absorbs the power of the cryptocurrency market, operating with greater stability as time goes by.  The Fund will also provide any token owner with an option at any time of its existence: the token owner will be allowed to retriever a % of the Fund total equity in exchange for the NICs, which then will be automatically burn in order to preserve the Fund - Token relation intact.  Take a look at the token documentation and get back to us if you have any doubt.  Thanks!

Anyone with an account can submit information to your page, so we are reaching out to this community to get you all involved in the discussion. Thanks! PS: If you have any questions about filling in the info, feel free to ask us in our discord group: https://discord.gg/j8RBAwB

Author: joiniconic
Title: [ANN][ICO] ICONIC - An ICOs ecosystem built through Decentralized Assurance
Body: Hi,  If the greatest feature of our project is the Assurance and all the security tools that Iconic will bring to the community, we need to highlight that our business provides a comprehensive plan to succeed not just for itself, but for our entire ecosystem, contributors and environment.  Iconic is providing a good opportunity for more than one profile of investor and user - both the trader as who would prefer to keep their token. For one side, Iconic's financial model contemplates not just a way to be profitable with an environment for another ICOs - as Iconic's Business Head said here https://goo.gl/5ZNrmu , a middleman for a middleman makes no sense in blockchain industry - but we think in every aspect of this process: The Offer, the aftermarket and the guarantees and security to show that decentralized does not have to be unorganized.  So, if we are talking just about the company, we believe that is a really well-designed and planned business that has all the tools to be successful  But, moreover, we offer a decentralized ballast fund on our coin that is called DAO NIC Fund, providing a strategy to make our investor have its assets valuing naturally with the development of Iconic's operation and relative business (ICOs, trading, audit, arbitration). It's a way to prove the value behind Iconic's own coin (NIC)  To finish, Iconic has an independent Escrow Manager to manage its funds to release it with fullfiment of milestones to show that its ICO is a way to expand and operates, not just to profit.  Please, fell free to make any questions and join our channels.
